        <title>Session #1 Overview</title>
        <contents>&lt;div style="width: 716px;"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img width="169" height="253" style="float: right; margin-left: 10px; margin-right: 10px;" alt="Overview - 3 business people discussing large plan document" src="@@PLUGINFILE@@/LTA-EI-S1a-Overview.jpg" /&gt;&lt;span style="color: #800080;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Session #1: Introduction to Explicit Instruction&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this session we will:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Overview the course goals and syllabus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Get to know the participants in this course.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define Explicit Instruction (EI).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Describe the characteristics and principles of EI.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify types of student needs that are addressed by EI.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Examine role of both students and the instructor in EI.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Let's get started by looking at the goals and syllabus for this course.&lt;/p&gt;
