        <title>Course Goals</title>
        <contents>&lt;div style="width: 716px;"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="color: #800080;"&gt;Goals for this Course&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Explicit Instruction (EI) is an approach suitable for addressing any student goal, skill or content area. This course is designed for adult education instructors working primarily with native English-speaking adults at all literacy levels, particularly those who face barriers to learning. It is also, however, an appropriate approach for use with ESL learners functioning at intermediate and higher levels of oral language skills.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Course Goals:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;to increase adult educators' understanding of explicit instruction, its key elements, applications, and purposes;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;to assist adult educators in planning lessons that incorporate the elements of explicit instruction; and&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;to help adult educators incorporate explicit instruction in to their everyday teaching practice.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="color: #800080;"&gt;Please take a moment to reflect on the above course goals, and consider how they align with your own needs.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="color: #993300;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;"&gt;&lt;img width="54" height="50" style="float: left; margin-left: 10px; margin-right: 10px;" alt=" Reflection icon - dark head profile with puzzle brain" src="@@PLUGINFILE@@/LTA-EI-Reflecticonsm.jpg" /&gt;&lt;em&gt;What are your own goals for this course? What do you hope to gain by participating in this professional development opportunity?&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;"&gt;Now we'll review the topics and learning activities planned for this course by taking a look a the course syllabus.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="color: #993300;"&gt;Click on the Next link below to continue.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="color: #993300;"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;</contents>
