        <title>Course Syllabus</title>
        <contents>&lt;div style="width: 716px;"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="color: #993300;"&gt;&lt;img width="182" height="214" style="float: right; margin-left: 10px; margin-right: 10px;" alt="Hand pointing to location on large map" src="@@PLUGINFILE@@/LTA-EI-S1a-syllabus.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The course syllabus provides an outline of course topics and activities designed to assist participants in meeting these goals. Please take a moment to review the Syllabus linked below. This will provide you with a “big picture” guide as you go through the course. As you review the course activities, consider how they relate to your own goals for this course, and any questions or concerns you may have.&lt;/p&gt;
